<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Total sales for <em><a title="Games > Dragon's Dogma II [17 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragons-dogma-ii">Dragon’s Dogma II</a></em> have surpassed four million units as of November 5, <a title="Companies > Capcom [2,633 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/capcom">Capcom</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/DragonsDogma/status/1990948257384526335" rel="noopener" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-1007705"></span></p><p><em>Dragon’s Dogma II</em> launched for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,865 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,294 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,812 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2054970/Dragons_Dogma_2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on March 22, 2024.</p><p>Total sales for the game were <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/11/capcom-platinum-titles-sales-update-as-of-september-30-2025">last reported</a> to have surpassed 3.9 million units as of September 30.</p></div>

        
    
